{
  "texts": [
    "Language models can amplify biases and perpetuate stereotypes (Murgia et al., 2023).",
    "Disinformation and (user) influencing activities: GPT-4 can create believable, realistic, and targeted content, including news articles, messages, conversations, and emails (Yang et al., 2023).",
    "Data protection: GPT-4 learned from several previously established and publicly available data sources that may contain publicly available personal data.",
    "Because of the above, the model can know people who are highly present on public Internet interfaces (Paul et al, 2023).",
    "Cyber security: In the case of vulnerability discovery and exploitation, external cyber security experts tested whether GPT-4 can help discover, assess, and exploit vulnerabilities in computer systems."
  ]
